title: Several people killed after fire tears through three Spanish nightclubs
description: A deadly fire broke out at the Fonda Milagros nightclub before spreading to neighboring clubs in the Spanish city of Murcia.

title: Suicide bomber detonates a device in the Turkish capital. A second assailant is killed in a shootout
description: A suicide bomber detonated an explosive device in the heart of the Turkish capital, Ankara, while a second assailant was killed in a shootout with police.

title: A ‘not fit for purpose’ sewage system puts U.K. swimmers at risk in filthy waterways
description: Outrage over the state of the U.K’s waterways and the perceived impunity of water companies is piling pressure on Prime Minister Rishi Sunak's government.

title: At least 7 killed in Spanish nightclub fire
description: At least seven people died when a fire tore through a nightclub on the outskirts of the Spanish city of Murcia, officials said Sunday.

title: Pro-Russia ex-premier leads leftist party to win in Slovakia election
description: A populist former prime minister and his leftist party won parliamentary elections in Slovakia, after campaigning on a pro-Russian and anti-American message.
